Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
