Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 years have passed since the \NWar of the Best in Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew each \Ncompleted individual training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on their way to the \Nnext stage - the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they reached the Fish-Man Island \Nlocated 10,000 meters below sea level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they have yet to gather and are \Nstirring things up as a fragmented crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna restore his dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the New Fish-Man Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No! I tell you this is no good!\N--What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie, do me a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! The water is rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask! \NLet those two get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can get away with \Nthat guy chasing after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand in my way of \Nconquering this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's big! Don't tell me that that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They kidnapped the Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Sanji! Don't turn around at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, you're gonna die, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:16.58,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Keep Shirahoshi Safe!\N Decken Close Behind!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming! To wherever my Shirahoshi is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dead or marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Princess Shirahoshi has...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...really been...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Coward! Why did you come out of Shark?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! Luffy-sama,\N please don't get mad at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made Princess-sama cry!\N What an evil pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel terrible... Princess Shirahoshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "Princess"! Don't tell me that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't turn around at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, could it be that the \NMermaid Princess is behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I turn around?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's there! That's why I don't\N want you to turn around, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost died after seeing\N some average Mermaids!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you see the Mermaid Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll lose all of your blood\N and it's curtains for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaid Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say even the most beautiful woman
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the world - Pirate Empress Boa \NHancock's looks pale in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the most gorgeous of all Mermaids.\N And now, she's behind my back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I beg you! Don't turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than live a day longer without\N grasping at a dream within reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will live out my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and choose to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I thought your dream\N was to go to the All Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know how poor my imagination is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a beauty that you can't even draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He turned to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta rescue her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:09:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're the Straw Hats who are \Nstrong enough to occupy the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he'd die from a nosebleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he turned to stone! That's new.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe because of his blood donors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy-sama, I don't know... what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Hachi, who did this to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you guys want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We caught them!\N--The Straw Hats! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are sea hunters who risk our lives\N to catch the Sea Kings everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are no match for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with the sea hunters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The Sea hunters did it!\N--Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are fishermen?! We're not fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you, too! You're the punk\N who used to be in Arlong's group!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe now, Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn them over to the Ammo Knights\N so they can cut their heads off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's not like that, everybody.\N Luffy-sama was not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys! \NSomething's flying towards us! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's no use--we're not gonna be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hey, something's really flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just some coral?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, somebody's on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you! I suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vander Decken-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've been hiding for a long time \Nand now he's finally showed himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess-sama, run! We'll handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want your answer, Shirahoshi! \NIf it's "Yes," you can escape death!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been throwing weapons \Nat her for 10 years to kill her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now you wanna marry her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around, Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess must have feared \Ndeath for 10 years because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you propose to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:12:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want your answer, Shirahoshi!\N I suspect it's "Yes"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wanna say?! "Yes"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is that the reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... Y... Y... Y...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:13:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You trampled on my feelings of 10 \Nyears and now who will you marry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't love me, \Nyour very existence irritates me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop dead, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! We'll stop him here with our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go anywhere! Stay there, Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?! \NWe can't trust you pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Decken's accomplice,\N aren't you? You want her to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run somewhere, I can't keep you safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, I'll stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How dare you scare her!\N--You evil pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry guys. I have nothing\N against you but you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it with his hands tied!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you wanna interfere with\N my business with Shirahoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who took Shirahoshi out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that's been throwing things at Coward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you both! Let me put you two \Ntogether and cut you into quarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...beat Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still moving but we can catch him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He turned to stone a while ago but \Nhe looks happy now. He's conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaid Princess... Am \NI in heaven or paradise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream came true! I can die now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, your dream was to go \Nto the All Blue, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't yell at me.\N It makes my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people on this island \Ndon't like us for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Coward! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Princess-sama, why did you untie him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That evil pirate must've scared her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, everybody! I \Nwill be back by dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away, you shits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wadatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Sea Bonze who attacked\N the Sunny! He works for Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I-It's the Great Monk!\N--Wadatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My front tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It cracked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's good for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coward, let's get to the Sea Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.71,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,DRAGON
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Hordy! A pirate girl and a Mermaid\N just exited the Ryugu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get rid of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there will be only an old \Nfool and a mob to take care of!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-chin, was it okay to leave \NZoro-chin and the others behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't escape with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! They always make it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know they're all tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hatchin said that Hordy is not only \Nstrong but has dangerous thoughts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've gotten much \Nstronger in last 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, what kind of person \Nis Jimbei, the former Warlord?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he is a pirate,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people on the island trust him so he's\N allowed to enter the Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. But he was in the same pirate\N group with Arlong, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy--Hordy is a follower of Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei's message to Luffy was \N"Don't fight against Hordy."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it because it's dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Zoro and the others won't make \NHordy mad as they get more involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any event, I wanna see Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be waiting for Luffy\N at the Sea Forest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The events happening now \Nhave deep roots in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could shake up the whole kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he knows everything\N about what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jimbei does?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the Sea Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! We'll get rid of Hordy\N and his crew immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I can't fight at full power, \Nyou'd be sacrificing your lives for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall give up the palace for now and \Nmeet up with Fukaboshi and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wait for a chance to fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up the palace? \NAre you serious, Neptune-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Zoro! He thinks he can \Nbeat a Fish-Man in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san, I keep losing my \Nstrength and I'm going to drown soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you starting to suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are so disadvantaged under water!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro's gonna pass out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what Hordy's up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm passing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That swordsman's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid is he? Thinking that a human\Ncan fight against a Fish-Man in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain in the ass. But this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop dead, you lowly creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Lion Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro's group must escape Ryugu Palace \Nbefore it fills with water,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the Fish-Men take Energy \NSteroids to enhance their strength
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.25,0:23:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and gain the upper hand again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Luffy's group has finally \Nreached Jimbei in the Sea Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he tells them of shocking past events\N involving Nami and Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Straw Hats Defeated?! \NHordy Gains Control of the Ryugu Palace!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
